item.title: King of Kings
item.description:
King of Kings

Jon Snow is a fictional character in the A Song of Ice and Fire series of fantasy novels by American author George R. R. Martin, and its television adaptation Game of Thrones . He is a prominent point of view character in the novels, and has been called one of the author's "finest creations" and most popular characters by The New York Times .
